{"tid":1628462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我明白著黑衫既原因 但","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T05:42:25.000Z","uid":41873,"like":41,"dislike":129,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"7cec08b497d39295875533ed35f7e2d166cc6bb6","tid":1628462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"(歡迎大家屌我)<br />\n<br />\n依家對家出到<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老屈</span></span></strong>手法<br />\n屈我地係暴徒<br />\n大肆破壞<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而開始有人動搖點解我地要咁做</span></span></strong><br />\n大家要承認既係 <br />\n可能真係有機會會令部份<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意轉向</span></span></strong>(當然我覺得只會係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極少部份</span></span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我覺得大家係唔係應該要考慮下每次行街都著唔同色衫呢(當然要配合足夠文宣)<br />\n例如今日著白色<br />\n下次行街著藍色<br />\n諸如此類<br />\n而且做文宣呼籲大家多用telegram等等其他工具</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然我地依家係有少少亂 但我相信所有人都係團結 發生任何事都唔會割蓆 就係因為我地仲係咁團結 我地一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">襯對家未轉為強勢</span></span></strong> 先下手為強 殺佢地一個片甲不留<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"370a30a8908c46a2971e2cc02b363e349273be5f","tid":1628462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1c69b7914cf8f90024a5abaaf88e8c85f00ace2","tid":1628462,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3a15fa93d12ac575a698e50657b7550faa6fae","tid":1628462,"uid":299104,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"